    "However, the VLM sometimes struggles to find the correct reference point (e.g., when the epidermis is torn or especially when it is ulcerated) or spatial orientation for the measurements, even though it recognizes the tumor mass itself (see Figure 4C, bottom; Supplementary Figure 5).",
